reviews.review_text: Recording review Terrific sounding recordings.  Nicely defined soundstage.  Drums have snap and body, vocals are clear, and Phil really rumbles.  Audience is present but not overpowering.  I did make a minor EQ adjustment to boost the bass.  This is an enjoyable recording.  Beautiful job by the recordist. Thank you.
